text: Tinizong-Rona was a municipality in the Albula district in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. It was formed in 1998 from the villages of Tinizong and Rona. The local administration was in Tinizong. Since 2016, became a part of the new Surses municipality. Category:Former municipalities of Graubünden
title: Tinizong-Rona
